OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FThe husband of a Labour MP is among
OL,8,Fthree men arrested in London and Wales
OL,9,Fon suspicion of spying for China and
OL,10,F"targeting UK democracy".
OL,12,FDavid Taylor, 39, was arrested
OL,13,Falongside two other men on Wednesday,
OL,14,Fand is married to Labour MP for East
OL,15,FKilbride and Strathaven Joani Reid.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said the
OL,8,Fsuspects ` aged 39, 43 and 68 ` were
OL,9,Farrested by counter-terrorism officers
OL,10,Fin London and Wales after being
OL,11,Faccused of assisting a foreign
OL,12,Fintelligence service.
OL,14,FTaylor is a lobbyist and the director
OL,15,Fof a PR, communications and
OL,16,Fconsultancy business called Earthcott
OL,17,FLimited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FHe is also the director of policy and
OL,8,Fprogrammes at Asia House, which is a
OL,9,FLondon-based think tank aiming to
OL,10,Fstrengthen economic ties between Asia,
OL,11,Fthe Middle East, and Europe.
OL,13,FResponding to reports of her husband's
OL,14,Farrest, Joani Reid said: "I have never
OL,15,Fseen anything to make me suspect my
OL,16,Fhusband has broken any law."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,F"I am not part of my husband's
OL,8,Fbusiness activities and neither I nor
OL,9,Fmy children are part of this
OL,10,Finvestigation, and we should not be
OL,11,Ftreated by media organisations as
OL,12,Fthough we are. Above all I expect
OL,13,Fmedia organisations to respect my
OL,14,Fchildren's privacy."
OL,16,FThe East Kilbride and Strathaven MP
OL,17,Fsaid: "I have never been to China. I
OL,18,Fhave never spoken on China or China-
OL,19,Frelated matters in the Commons. I have
OL,20,Fnever asked a question on China-
OL,21,Frelated matters.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@TO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,F"As far as I am aware I have never met
OL,8,Fany Chinese businesses whilst I have
OL,9,Fbeen an MP, any Chinese diplomats or
OL,10,Fgovernment employees, nor raised any
OL,11,Fconcern with ministers or anyone else
OL,12,Fon behalf of, even coincidentally,
OL,13,FChinese interests.
OL,15,F"I am a social democrat who believes
OL,16,Fin freedom of expression, free trade
OL,17,Funions and free elections. I am not
OL,18,Fany sort of admirer or apologist for
OL,19,Fthe Chinese Communist Party's
OL,20,Fdictatorship."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FAll three men remain in custody, and
OL,8,Fsearches have been carried out at the
OL,9,Faddresses where they were arrested,
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,12,FChinese officials in the UK and
OL,13,FBeijing have been given a dressing
OL,14,Fdown, a minister told MPs.
OL,16,FUpdating the Commons, security
OL,17,Fminister Dan Jarvis said there will be
OL,18,F"severe consequences" if it is proven
OL,19,Fthat China attempted to interfere with
OL,20,FUK sovereign affairs.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FJarvis said the investigation "relates
OL,8,Fto China" and "foreign interference
OL,9,Ftargeting UK democracy".
OL,11,FHe told MPs: "Let me be clear, if
OL,12,Fthere is proven evidence of attempts
OL,13,Fby China to interfere with UK
OL,14,Fsovereign affairs, we will impose
OL,15,Fsevere consequences and hold all
OL,16,Factors involved to account.
OL,18,F"The Government is taking robust
OL,19,Faction to ensure the UK's democratic
OL,20,Finstitutions and processes are a hard
OL,21,Ftarget for this activity.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@IO]pD@OOUqD@WO]sD@NOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
