CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,F"The National Security Act provides
OL,8,Four intelligence agencies and law
OL,9,Fenforcement with the modern legal
OL,10,Ftools they need to deter, detect and
OL,11,Fdisrupt the full range of state
OL,12,Fthreats.
OL,14,F"The action counter-terrorism police
OL,15,Fhave been able to take this morning is
OL,16,Fan example that that legislation is
OL,17,Fworking well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
