OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,13,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We have seen a significant
OL,15,Fincrease in our casework relating to
OL,16,Fnational security in recent years, and
OL,17,Fwe continue to work extremely closely
OL,18,Fwith our partners to help keep the
OL,19,Fcountry safe and take action to
OL,20,Fdisrupt malign activity where we
OL,21,Fsuspect it."
OL,26,@vD@GOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
