PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FIn addition to the addresses where the
OL,8,Fsuspects were arrested, the Met said
OL,9,Fthree other properties in London, East
OL,10,FKilbride in Scotland, and Cardiff have
OL,11,Falso been searched.
OL,13,FThe force said the 39-year-old suspect
OL,14,Fwas arrested in London, the 43-year-
OL,15,Fold man was arrested in Pontyclun in
OL,16,FSouth Wales, and the 68-year-old was
OL,17,Farrested in the county of Powys in mid-
OL,18,FWales ` with all three being detained
OL,19,Funder the Police and Criminal Evidence
OL,20,FAct.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772668984
OL,3,CHusband of Labour MP among three men
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FFlanagan added: "Today's arrests are
OL,8,Fpart of a proactive investigation and
OL,9,Fwhile these are serious matters, we do
OL,10,Fnot believe there to be any imminent
OL,11,For direct threat to the public
OL,12,Frelating to this.
OL,14,F"Our investigation continues and we
OL,15,Fthank the public for their ongoing
OL,16,Fsupport."
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOUxD@IO]
