OL,7,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"On Wednesday March 4 2026, we carried
OL,9,Fout a search of an address in East
OL,10,FKilbride on behalf of an investigation
OL,11,Fbeing led by Counter Terrorism
OL,12,FPolicing London."
